columnConfigurations.columnName: PR items created later than sales order items (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: PR items created later than sales order items (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until PO items created (days)",
    "Time until supplier invoice created (days)",
    "Time until customer Invoice items created (days)",
    "PR items created later than sales order items (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Purchase order items created") 
        	AS "Time until PO items created (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Supplier invoice created") 
        	AS "Time until supplier invoice created (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Customer Invoice items created") 
        	AS "Time until customer Invoice items created (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Purchase requisition items created later than sales order items") * 100 
        	AS "PR items created later than sales order items (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
